@startuml
title Compiled DAG 执行主流程

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName "PingFang SC"
skinparam ranksep 45
skinparam nodesep 30

left to right direction

[Planner\n内部完成 motion + TOPPRA\n输出 Compiled DAG\nActionNode(kind, q,dq,duration)\nWaitNode(feedback target)] as Planner
[Executor\n按 DAG deps/resources 调度\n启动 ready Action] as Executor
[RuntimeMixer\n每帧合并 active actions\nchassis + arm + flags] as Mixer
[Protocol/Client\npack_frame\n14 float + flags + CRC-8] as Client
node "下位机 MCU\n闭环控制 / 到位反馈" as MCU

Planner --> Executor : Compiled DAG
Executor --> Mixer : active actions
Mixer --> Client : 当前整车目标
Client --> MCU : 控制帧
MCU --> Executor : feedback\n满足 WaitNode 后解锁后继节点

note bottom of Planner
Planner 输出前已完成：
- 小 motion 生成几何路径
- TOPPRA 时间规划
- ActionNode 写入 q/dq/duration
end note

note bottom of Executor
执行阶段只看 DAG：
- ActionNode ready 后启动
- WaitNode 只由反馈满足
- 资源冲突禁止并行
不 import TOPPRA。
end note

note bottom of Mixer
每帧合并当前 active actions。
不能预先生成整段整车帧，
因为 WaitNode 何时满足取决于 MCU feedback。
end note

@enduml
